Library requirements for Inguma
-------------------------------

Inguma requires the following libraries in order for all the modules to work:

	* Impacket
	* Scapy
	* Paramiko
	* pysnmp
    * python-bluez

For the GTK+ user interface, please install:

    * GTK+3
    * GObject
    * graphviz
    * python-vte
    * python-imaging

Many modules will work without these libraries BUT the most interesting
modules will requires these libraries. At least is recommended to have
installed in your box Impacket, Scapy and Paramiko.

